headline.print_headline: EU to Prepare 'Next Level' of Russia Sanctions: Germany's Gabriel
headline.main: EU to Prepare 'Next Level' of Russia Sanctions: Germany's Gabriel

lead_paragraph: European Union leaders have agreed to prepare "the next level of sanctions" against Russia in response to its intervention in Ukraine, German Vice-Chancellor Sigmar Gabriel said on Saturday.
